Explanations:
The purpose of the documents in this folder is to dive further into the
detail of specific concepts. It is meant to give those reading the
information a deeper knowledge of how something works, why something was built, or the
reason for decisions. These articles are meant to be linked to from other articles where
it would not fit to go into further discussion about a topic.

Guideline:
- Provide detail to understand a problem, solution, and testing around that solution



The reason for x is because historically, y…
    Explain.

W is better than z, because…
    Offer judgements and even opinions where appropriate..

An x in system y is analogous to a w in system z. However…
    Provide context that helps the reader.

Some users prefer w (because z). This can be a good approach, but…
    Weigh up alternatives.

An x interacts with a y as follows:…
    Unfold the machinery’s internal secrets, to help understand why something does what it does.
